- Location Preference for Insights: "Remote (USA)" (Or specific city/state, e.g., "San Francisco, CA")
- Desired Seniority Level for Insights: "Senior" (e.g., Junior, Mid-Level, Senior, Lead)


- Resume Content: (String/Text) - The User model links to a Resume model, indicating resume content is likely uploaded or entered.


